data.description: Welcome to this stunning 20-acre farmstead with lake frontage, offering an idyllic countryside retreat. This charming property boasts a spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with vaulted ceilings and an inviting open concept design. With a 2-stall attached garage, your vehicles and equipment are easily accessible. A standout feature of this farmstead is the 32x56 shop, providing ample space for storage, workshops, or even a home-based business. Additionally, the property includes a chicken coop and barn with approximately 15 acres of fenced and divided pasture land. Nestled on the edge of a tranquil lake, this farmstead offers breathtaking views and a peaceful ambiance lending to a unique opportunity to experience a quintessential farm lifestyle only 35 minutes from the FM area
